    "name": "Saigon Prince Hotel",
    "detail": "This hotel is in very strategic location in front of Ho Chi Minh Square in the middle of crowded area. Shopping malls are only 5 minutes walk. Food are very easy to find around hotel, although meal price is high in Ho Chi Minh City. Breakfast if good. Hotel staff is very kind, they bring breakfast to our room due to one of our family is not very well. Hotel also pack breakfast for our family members who take very early flight , it is amazing and very excellent service of this hotel. I will stay again in this hotel if I come back to HCM. Hotel room rate is not very high, it is value for money. I recommend this excellent hotel to any one who visits HCM City. WIFI Is fast. TV Programme is also good.",
