    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/ngan-ha-hotel/hotel/ho-chi-minh-city-vn.html",
    "name": "Nicecy Ngan Ha Hotel",
    "detail": "Also known as Milky Way Hotel, the hotel signboard is not so obvious so you may miss it sometimes. Just look for AVANTI hotel and Ngan Ha is next to it. Good location, walkable distances to many attactions such as Ben Thanh Market (just opposite the hotel), HCM City Museum (400m), HCM City Museum of Fine Arts (500m), Independence Palace (750m), Huynh Hoa Sandwich Shop (600m, ppl said it's the best banh mi in HCM), pho 2000 (150m), Pizza 4P's (170m). Limited breakfast choices (just 3 choices), but it's ok you can hunt various breakfast nearby. Stayed in the room with small window facing the hotel's staircase, it's abit too bright as no blackout curtain blocking the staircase light. Oh ya, the elevator reach 8th floor only, and you need to climb few steps to reach 9th floor (the small restaurant for breakfast). As my room is on 8th floor, it's abit noisy when people walking up to 9th floor for breakfast. Friendly service, smooth check in and check out. ",
